[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     'described\n'
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     'in the Observation. The '
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     'various types of objects '
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     'in the kitchen include\n'
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     '- Station: A location in '
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     'the kitchen where you can '
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     'perform special actions, '
[36m(TaskRunner pid=3495154)[0m                                                     'e.g. cooking or cutting\n'
